Silence::

"Eh, uh, so...uh...how many more of you are there here? I mean, by the
way you speak, there are more than yourself and Megatron?"  She felt
uneasy. Having so many Predacons and Decepticons in the Maximal base,
it was almost too much for her.  Though she couldn't figure out why.
It was logical to combine forces to win against such a strong foe. Yet
deep in her spark, she couldn't trust them.
